    - [round_05up_class,       decimal.ROUND_05UP.__class__.__name__,       [],  "str",  "decimal.ROUND_05UP.__class__.__name__ == 'str'; ROUND_05UP is a plain Python str constant; confirmed Python 3.14.3 macOS"]

